--> ESP32 Devkit
Processor: ESP32-WROOM-32 module
CPU: Dual-core Tensilica LX6 32-bit microprocessor with clock frequency up to 240 MHz
SRAM: 520 KB
ROM: 448 KB
RTC SRAM: 16 KB
Connectivity:
- 802.11 b/g/n Wi-Fi
--- Supported data rates: up to 150 Mbps
--- Supported security protocols: WPA2/WPA3
--- Supported features: station mode, AP mode, mesh mode
- Bluetooth 4.2 BR/EDR and BLE
--- Bluetooth 4.2 BR/EDR and BLE
--- Supported features: classic Bluetooth, Bluetooth Low Energy
--- Supported profiles: SPP, GATT, A2DP, AVRCP, HFP, HID
Peripherals:
- 34 GPIO pins
- 12 ADC channels
- 2 DAC channels
- 2 I2S channels
- 3 SPI channels
- 2 UART channels
- I2C master and slave
- Ethernet MAC
- Touch sensor
- Hall sensor
- SD card interface
- IR receiver
- IR transmitter
- Camera interface
- LCD interface
- Power supply:
- 5V DC input
- 3.3V DC output
LDO regulator
Dimensions: 51.8 x 25.4 mm
Weight: 10 g

16 Pin + 2 GND & VCC
ESP32 GPIO D15 (HSPI) -> DC TFT Display
ESP32 GPIO D2 (HSPI CS) -> RES TFT Display
ESP32 GPIO D23 (SPI MOSI) -> SDA TFT Display
ESP32 GPIO D18 (SPI CLK) -> SCL TFT Display

ESP32 GPIO D4 (Software Serial as RX) -> DF Player TX 
ESP32 GPIO D5 (Software Serial as TX) -> DF Player RX

ESP32 GPIO D16 (RX2) -> TX PN532 RFID module
ESP32 GPIO D17 (TX2) -> RX PN532 RFID module

ESP32 GPIO D22 -> Push button input

ESP32 GPIO D36 (Sensor VP) -> Analog Read TCRT5000
ESP32 GPIO D39 (Sensor VN) -> Analog Read LJ12A34Z
ESP32 GPIO D13 (PWM) -> Motor Servo

ESP32 GPIO D32 -> Clock input IC Shift Register 74Hc595
ESP32 GPIO D33 -> Latch Pin input IC Shift Register 74Hc595
ESP32 GPIO D25 -> Serial Data input IC Shift Register 74Hc595

ESP32 GPIO D12 -> Potensiometer for volume control DF player

Adafruit_GFX.h (TFT Display)
Adafruit_ST7789.h (TFT Display seri ST7789)
Arduino.h (Arduino core libary)
DFRobotDFPlayerMini.h (DF player)
ESP32Servo.h (Motor Servo)
PN532.h (PN532 RFID)
PN532_HSU.h (PN532 RFID with UART)
SPI.h (SPI connect TFT Display)
SoftwareSerial.h (Software Serial connect DF player)
millisDelay.h (Simple Delay strategy)
ShiftRegister74HC595.h (Shift Register 74HC595)
qrcode.h (Generate byres of QR Code)
WiFi.h (WiFi connectifity)
PubSubClient.h (MQTT Client)
